                            <comment id="15425971" author="dongjoon" created="Thu, 18 Aug 2016 06:37:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You can see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-17053&quot; title=&quot;Spark ignores hive.exec.drop.ignorenonexistent=true option&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPARK-17053&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPARK-17053&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, too.&lt;br/&gt;
